name: Version 1.6 for Minecraft 1.18
body: - Deprecated the Enchantment Cracker in favour of clientcommands. The external tool will still be supported for those who prefer not to use a mod.

name: Version 1.5.1 for Minecraft 1.8-1.17.1
body:
- Added chainmail option.
- Added support for 32-bit Java and improved memory footprint.
- Fixed DPI scaling when it shouldn't.
- Fixed a rare false negative.
- Added new language translations: Polish, Traditional Chinese, French, improved German.

name: Version 1.5 for Minecraft 1.8-1.16
body:
* Added support for 1.16
* Added support for translations
  - Added German, Chinese (Mandarin) and Russian translations.
  - Contributions to translations are welcome, including new languages or improvements to already translated languages.
  - To contribute a translation, look for an existing language file [here](https://github.com/Earthcomputer/EnchantmentCracker/tree/master/resources/i18n), translate it into your own language, and send me the language file via an issue or pull request.

name: Version 1.4.6
body:
- Indicate that 1.15 is supported
- Fix a minor GUI bug

name: Version 1.4.5
body:
- Add setting for current player XP amount
- Fix memory back to 2GB, and add an error message for allocation problems on startup.
- Fix #109 - crash when clicking to the right of the about tab

name: Version 1.4.4
body:
- Fix most book enchantments and sweeping edge and unbreaking on swords being broken
- Change default memory allocation again

name: Version 1.4.3
body:
- Better focus traversal
- Revert "smart" item throw amount algorithm
- Fix text position

name: Version 1.4.1 for Minecraft 1.8-1.14.4
body:
- Fix riptide 3 being impossible
- Add multi-version support
- Add more tooltips
- JVM flags to increase memory enabled by default
- Better log output

name: Version 1.4 for Minecraft 1.14.3-1.14.4
body:
- Update to 1.14.3
- New Look and Feel thanks to @Hexicube!

name: Version 1.3 for Minecraft 1.14-1.14.2
body:
- Added crossbow and enchantments
- Updated enchantment algorithm to 1.14.2
- Now works on OSX

name: Version 1.2.1 for Minecraft 1.13-1.13.2
body:
- Add turtle helmet
- UI improvements by @asquared31415

name: Version 1.1.4 for Minecraft 1.11.1-1.12.2
body: * Fixed a couple of out of memory issues

name: Version 1.1.3 for Minecraft 1.11.1 - 1.12.2
body:
* Fixed #9 again
* Add a Java implementation of the XP seed cracker for people on 32-bit and also as a temporary solution for people on Mac OS

name: Version 1.1.2
body:
* Fixed #8 - Crash if not specifying level for non-single-level enchantments
* Fixed #9 - Enchant cracker sometimes crashes if you go from second tab to first tab
* You now no longer need to specify the level of enchantments

name: Version 1.1.1 for Minecraft 1.11.1 - 1.12.2
body: * Fixed a dependency on a Java 9 function. It should now run in Java 8 again. (#7)

name: Version 1.1 for Minecraft 1.11.1 - 1.12.2
body:
+ Added an information tab
+ Added the ability to clear unwanted enchantments
+ Added a log
* Fixed #2 - Helmet enchantments can't be predicted on helmets
* Fixed #3 - Cracker predicts too many enchantments on books
* Fixed #4 - Bow enchantments error prediction
* Increased search limit for items thrown from 1000 to 10000
* Tooltips to make it easier to use
* An actual error message instead of an UnsatisfiedLinkError

name: Version 1.0.1 for Minecraft 1.11.1-1.12.2
body: Fixed "Unable to access jarfile enchcracker.jar" on Windows if there are spaces in the path
